%20were%20in%20our%2020s%2C%20we%20moved%20in%20with%20Billy%20and%20Fern%2C%20a%20couple%20in%20their%2050s.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20was%20a%20great%20living%20situation%2C%20and%20we%20became%20close%20during%20our%20time%20renting%20a%20room%20from%20them.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThough%20we've%20since%20moved%20on%2C%20we've%20remained%20lifelong%20friends.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20were%20in%20our%2020s%2C%20my%20partner%20Sam%20and%20I%20decided%20to%20do%20a%20working%20holiday%20in%20Banff%2C%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20we%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarried-couple-roommate-afford-dream-apartment-rent-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erented%20a%20room%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20three-bedroom%20share%20house%20with%20two%20other%20couples%20who%20were%20close%20in%20age%20to%20us.%20It%20was%20loads%20of%20fun%2C%20but%20nobody%20did%20much%20cleaning%2C%20and%20there%20was%20a%20fair%20amount%20of%20drinking%20and%20partying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESam%20got%20a%20job%20with%20the%20town%20of%20Banff%20and%20soon%20he%20befriended%20this%20Canadian%20guy%20named%20Billy.%20Billy%20is%20one%20of%20those%20larger-than-life%20personalities%3B%20he's%20high%20energy%20and%20extremely%20likeable.%20Everyone%20in%20town%20knows%20him%2C%20and%20he's%20affectionately%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BBilly%20Banff.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20day%2C%20Billy%20mentioned%20that%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Froommates-30s-cheap-rent-company-pros-cons-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehad%20a%20room%20available%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20their%20cozy%20two-bedroom%20property.%20After%20chatting%20with%20me%20about%20it%2C%20Sam%20told%20Billy%20we'd%20love%20to%20take%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c5940169-e009-4db4-a20d-c2cd3f27b543%5C%22%3EWe%20lived%20together%20well%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20never%20forget%20the%20day%20we%20moved%20in.%20I%20me