20Morning%20Consult%20poll%20found%20that%20Musk's%20net%20favorability%20is%20at%20-14%20percentage%20points.%20The%20good%20news%20for%20the%20billionaire%20is%20that%20his%20overall%20standing%20as%20of%20June%2020%20is%20up%20four%20points%20since%20June%2015%2C%20the%20week%20after%20the%20peak%20of%20his%20feud%20with%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20still%20lower%20than%20where%20he%20stood%20when%20he%20left%20the%20White%20House%20in%20late%20May.%20Among%20Republicans%2C%20Musk%20is%20down%20roughly%2012%20points%3B%20he'd%20dropped%2010%20points%20immediately%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fa-timeline-of-how-elon-musks-relationship-with-trump-imploded-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20criticized%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20early%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20US%2C%20Musk%20managed%20to%20alienate%20both%20those%20on%20the%20left%20(due%20to%20his%20support%20for%20DOGE%2C%20the%20Trump%20administration%2C%20and%20the%20election)%20and%20those%20on%20the%20right%20(as%20seen%20in%20his%20statements%20on%20X%20following%20his%20fallout%20with%20the%20President%20over%20the%20%26quot%3Bbig%20beautiful%20bill%26quot%3B)%2C%26quot%3B%20Frank%20T.%20Rothaermel%2C%20a%20regents'%20professor%20at%20the%20Scheller%20College%20of%20Business%20at%20Georgia%20Tech%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20good%20thing%20in%20the%20US%20is%20that%20people's%20memories%20are%20short%20and%20a%20ton%20of%20stuff%20is%20happening%20every%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVoters%20began%20to%20become%20increasingly%20polarized%20toward%20Musk%20after%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-twitter-reach-agreement-to-close-acquisition-deal-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etakeover%20of%20Twitter%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Morning%20Consult%20US%20Politics%20Analyst%20Eli%20Yokley%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Musk's%20closeness%20to%20Trump%20%26quot%3Bpoured%20fuel%20on%20the%20fire%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20left%20his%20image%20in%20a%20much%20different%20state%20than%20some%20of%20his%20fellow%20tech%20moguls%2C%20who%20also%20sought%20to%20curry%20favor%20with%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20weighs%20on%20him%20in%20a%20very%20unique%20way%20that%20other%20CEOs%20who%20have%20tried%20to%20kiss%20the%20ring%20a%20bit%20just%20haven't%20experienced%20to%20the%20same%20extent%2C%26quot%3B%20Yokley%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk's%20favorability%20isn't%20polled%20as%20frequently%20as%20someone%20like%20Trump.%20YouGov%2C%20which%20has%20sporadic%20data%20on%20Musk%20going%20back%20to%202018%2C%20found%20that%20immediately%20after%20the%20feud%2C%20Musk%20recorded%20his%20lowest%20net%20favorability%20in%20its%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20handful%20of%20post-feud%20polls%20that%20have%20been%20released%20show%20similar%20warning%20signs.%20Namely%2C%20many%20Republicans%2C%20who%20were%20once%20the%20bulwark%20for%20Musk's%20sagging%20numbers%2C%20no%20longer%20have%20such%20rosy%20views%20of%20the%20billionaire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Economist-YouGov%20poll%20taken%20in%20the%20week%20after%20the%20feud%20found%20that%20Musk's%20net%20favorability%20among%20Republicans%20dropped%2020%20points.%20A%20Reuters-Ipsos%20poll%20found%20that%20he%20dropped%2013%20points%20in%20net%20favorability%20in%20a%20roughly%20one-month%20span.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2Fxkx62%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Views%20of%20Elon%20Musk%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22457%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22394e1789-be98-4da8-ac69-290d98356a80%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20a%20critical%20moment%20for%20Tesla%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20June%