ll.%20Then%2C%20out%20of%20nowhere%2C%20M3GAN%20begins%20to%20sing%20to%20Gemma%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUXzx--YefD8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKate%20Bush's%20late%201980s%20hit%20single%20%26quot%3BThis%20Woman's%20Work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20M3GAN%20belts%20out%20the%20song%2C%20Gemma%20commands%20her%20creation%20to%20stop%20singing.%20But%20M3GAN%20keeps%20on%20going%2C%20pressing%20two%20of%20her%20robotic%20fingers%20on%20Gemma's%20lips%20to%20silence%20her%20as%20she%20sings%20on.%20Even%20a%20full%20orchestra%20kicks%20in%20to%20heighten%20the%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20laugh-out-loud%20moment%20that%20writer-director%20Gerard%20Johnstone%20knew%20would%20work%2C%20going%20all%20the%20way%20back%20to%20when%20he%20put%20it%20in%20an%20early%20draft%20of%20the%20script.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20two%20things%20about%20the%20first%20movie%20that%20defined%20it%2C%20M3GAN's%20singing%20and%20her%20dancing%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnstone%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20knew%20that%20as%20much%20as%20I%20wanted%20to%20change%20things%20up%20on%20this%20one%2C%20I%20had%20to%20figure%20out%20a%20way%20to%20do%20those%20two%20things.%20It%20was%20so%20delightful%20that%20we%20kind%20of%20pulled%20it%20off%20and%20got%20the%20moment%20that%20we%20were%20hoping%20for.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fm3gan-dance-scene-not-in-original-script-megan-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efirst%20movie%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20M3GAN%20has%20her%20dance%20moment%20in%20the%20sequel%2C%20but%20this%20time%2C%20it's%20her%20singing%20that%20is%20the%20highlight%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Johnstone%20knew%20the%20Bush%20song%20would%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20a%20few%20conversations%20with%20my%20producers%20about%20using%20that%20song%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20I%20just%20felt%20there's%20something%20about%20it%2C%20the%20way%20Kate%20Bush%20writes%20music%2C%20no%20one%20else%20writes%20music%20that%20way%2C%20so%20I%20thought%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20odd%2C%20but%20people%20are%20going%20to%20love%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b669c9ec-37d2-4213-a340-ecd08cfb7625%5C%22%3EThe%20singing%20scene%20was%20done%20with%20a%20fully%20animatronic%20M3GAN%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Robot%20Megan%20on%20set%20of%20movie%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685d2aebf748d8c055f46534%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BM3GAN%202.0%26quot%3B%20director%20Gerard%20Johnstone%20on%20set%20with%20an%20animatronic%20M3GAN.%3Cp%3EUniversal%20Pictures%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20singing%20sequence%20also%20showcases%20the%20evolution%20of%20the%20robotics%20used%20for%20M3GAN%20compared%20to%20the%20first%20movie%2C%20as%20Williams%20acted%20across%20from%20an%20animatronic%20puppet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20our%20animatronic%20M3GAN%20doing%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnstone%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20recorded%20those%20lines%20leading%20up%20to%20that%20moment.%20The%20song%20itself%20was%20sung%20by%20Jenna%20Davis%2C%20who%20voices%20M3GAN.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20there%20were%20three%20puppeteers%20behind%20M3GAN%20helping%20to%20position%20her%20body%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnstone%20continued.%20%26quot%3BA%20puppeteer's%20arm%20is%20M3GAN's%20arm%20in%20that%20moment%2C%20to%20do%20some%20of%20the%20moves%20like%20putting%20her%20two%20fingers%20on%20Gemma's%20lips.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohnstone%20said%20the%20animatronic%20lip%20sync%20was%20so%20spot%20on%20that%20Williams%20had%20to%20make%20sure%20her%20timing%20was%20right%20in%20the%20scene%20when%20she%20delivered%20her%20lines%2C%20even%20when%20the%20voice%20coming%20out%20of%20M3GAN%20would%20