s%20that%20will%20prove%20we've%20reached%20AGI%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20PR%20departments%20of%20OpenAI%20and%20Anthropic%20use%20their%20own%20AI%20technology%20to%20answer%20every%20journalist's%20question.%20Right%20now%2C%20these%20companies%20are%20hiring%20a%20ton%20of%20human%20journalists%20and%20other%20communications%20experts%20to%20handle%20a%20barrage%20of%20reporter%20questions%20about%20AI%20and%20the%20future.%20When%20I%20reach%20out%20to%20these%20companies%2C%20humans%20answer%20every%20time.%20Unacceptable!%20Unless%20this%20changes%2C%20we're%20not%20at%20AGI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20suggestion%20is%20from%20a%20hedge%20fund%20contact%2C%20and%20I%20love%20it%3A%20Please%2C%20please%20can%20my%20Microsoft%20Outlook%20email%20system%20stop%20burying%20important%20emails%20while%20still%20letting%20spam%20through%3F%20This%20one%20seems%20like%20something%20Microsoft%20and%20OpenAI%20could%20solve%20with%20their%20AI%20technology.%20I%20haven't%20seen%20a%20fix%20yet.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20a%20similar%20vein%2C%20can%20someone%20please%20stop%20Cactus%20Warehouse%20from%20texting%20me%20every%202%20days%20with%20offers%20for%2020%25%20off%20succulents%3F%20I%20only%20bought%20one%20cactus%20from%20you%20guys%20once!%20Come%20on%2C%20AI%2C%20this%20can%20surely%20be%20solved!%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMy%202024%20Tesla%20Model%203%20Performance%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-fsd-diary-curiosity-amazement-shock-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehits%20potholes%20in%20FSD%3C%2Fa%3E.%20No%20wonder%20tires%20have%20to%20be%20replaced%20so%20often%20on%20these%20EVs.%20As%20a%20human%2C%20I%20can%20avoid%20potholes%20much%20better.%20Elon%2C%20the%20AGI%20gauntlet%20has%20been%20thrown%20down.%20Get%20on%20this%20%3Cem%3Enow%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECan%20AI%20models%20and%20chatbots%20make%20valuable%20predictions%20about%20the%20future%2C%20or%20do%20they%20mostly%20just%20regurgitate%20what's%20already%20known%20on%20the%20internet%3F%20I%20tested%20this%20recently%2C%20right%20after%20the%20US%20bombed%20Iran.%20ChatGPT's%20stock-picking%20ability%20was%20put%20to%20the%20test%20versus%20a%20single%20human%20analyst.%20Check%20out%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftampon-trade-chatgpt-dan-ives-stock-market-predictions-us-iran-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eresults%20here%3C%2Fa%3E.%20TL%3BDR%3A%20We%20are%20nowhere%20near%20AGI%20on%20this%20one.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThere's%20a%20great%20Google%20Gemini%20TV%20ad%20where%20a%20kid%20is%20helping%20his%20dad%20assemble%20a%20basketball%20net.%20The%20son%20is%20using%20an%20Android%20phone%20to%20ask%20Gemini%20for%20the%20instructions%20and%20pointing%20the%20camera%20at%20his%20poor%20father%20struggling%20with%20parts%20and%20tools.%20It's%20really%20impressive%20to%20watch%20as%20Gemini%20finds%20the%20instruction%20manual%20online%20just%20by%20%26quot%3Bseeing%26quot%3B%20what's%20going%20on%20live%20with%20the%20product%20assembly.%20For%20AGI%20to%20be%20here%2C%20though%2C%20the%20AI%20needs%20to%20just%20%3Cem%3Ebuild%20the%20damn%20net%20itself%3C%2Fem%3E.%20I%20can%20sit%20there%20and%20read%20out%20instructions%20in%20an%20annoying%20way%2C%20while%20someone%20else%20toils%20with%20fiddly%20assembly%20tasks%20%E2%80%94%20we%20can%20all%20do%20that.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20I%20know%20these%20tests%20seem%20a%20bit%20silly%20%E2%80%94%20but%20AI%20benchmarks%20are%20not%20the%20real%20world%2C%20and%20they%20can%20be%20pretty%20easily%20gamed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20last%20basketball%20net%20test%20is%20particularly%20telling%20for%20me.%20Getting%20an%20AI%20system%20and%20software%20to%20actually%20assemble%20a%20basketball%20net%20%E2%80%94%20that%20might%20happen%20sometime%20soon.%20But%2C%20getting%20the%20same%20system%20to%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20other%20physical-world%20manipulation%20stuff%20better%20than%20humans%2C%20too%3F%20Very%20hard%20and%20probably%20not%20possible%20for%20a%20very%20long%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20OpenAI%20and%20Microsoft%20try%20to%20resolve%20their%20differences%2C%20the%20companies%20can%20tap%20experts%20to%20weigh%20in%20on%20whether%20the%20startup%20has%20reached%20AGI%20or%20not%2C%20per%20the%20terms%20of%20their%20existing%20contract%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Information.%20I'm%20happy%20to%20be%20an%20expert%20advisor%20here.%20Sam%20and%20Satya%2C%20let%20me%20know%20if%20you%20want%20help!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20I'll%20leave%20the%20final%20words%20to%20a%20real%20AI%20expert.%20Konstantin%20Mishchenko%2C%20an%20AI%20research%20scientist%20at%20Meta%2C%20recently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fkonstmish%2Fstatus%2F1934208217980022913%3Fs%3D46%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etweeted%20this%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20citing%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsergeylevine.substack.com%2Fp%2Flanguage-models-in-platos-cave%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblog%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20another%20respected%20expert%20in%20the%20field%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fsvlevine%2Fstatus%2F1931796654233194534%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESergey%20Levine%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20LLMs%20learned%20to%20mimic%20intelligence%20from%20internet%20data%2C%20they%20never%20had%20to%20actually%20live%20and%20acquire%20that%20intelligence%20directly.%20They%20lack%20the%20core%20algorithm%20for%20learning%20from%20experience.%20They%20need%20a%20human%20to%20do%20that%20work%20for%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Mishchenko%20wrote%2C%20referring%20to%20AI%20models%20known%20as%20large%20language%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20suggests%2C%20at%20least%20to%20me%2C%20that%20the%20gap%20between%20LLMs%20and%20genuine%20intelligence%20might%20be%20wider%20than%20we%20think.%20Despite%20all%20the%20talk%20about%20AGI%20either%20being%20already%20here%20or%20coming%20next%20year%2C%20I%20can't%20shake%20off%20the%20feeling%20it's%20not%20possible%20until%20we%20come%20up%20with%20something%20better%20than%20a%20language%20model%20mimicking%20our%20own%20idea%20of%20how%20an%20AI%20should%20look%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESign%20up%20for%20BI's%20Tech%20Memo%20newsletter%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Ftech-memo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ehere%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%20Reach%20out%20to%20me%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabarr%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eabarr%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-microsoft-duel-agi-real-world-tests-ai-better-humans-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751187601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685efa10f748d8c055f49318%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-microsoft-duel-agi-real-world-tests-ai-better-humans-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20most%20important%20AI%20partnership%20in%20the%20world%20partly%20revolves%20around%20whether%20OpenAI%20achieves%20AGI.%20I%20propose%20several%20practical%20tests.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abarr%40businessinsider.com%20(Alistair%20Barr)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A102%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-microsoft-duel-agi-real-world-tests-ai-better-humans-2025-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20new%20must-have%20for%20CEOs%3A%20An%20AI%20whisperer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225334%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Executives%20jumping%20from%20a%20human%20hand%20and%20to%20a%20robotic%20hand%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685d99053d5881a51c1c2af1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223001%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EExecutive%20advisers%20say%20they%20have%20waiting%20lists%20of%20CEOs%20who%20want%20help%20incorporating%20AI%20into%20their%20companies.%3Cp%3Esesame%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ELeaders%20are%20seeking%20guidance%20on%20everything%20from%20vetting%20AI%20vendors%20to%20establishing%20safety%20protocols.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20May%20survey%20found%20that%2088%25%20of%20senior%20executives%20plan%20to%20increase%20their%20AI-related%20budgets.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BCEOs%20need%20an%20AI%20translator%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lan%20Guan%2C%20Accenture's%20chief%20AI%20officer.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20year%20ago%2C%20Glenn%20Hopper%20was%20advising%20just%20a%20handful%20of%20company%20leaders%20on%20how%20to%20embed%20AI%20agents%20and%20tools%20like%20ChatGPT%20throughout%20their%20organizations.%20Today%2C%20the%20Memphis-based%20AI%20strategist%20has%20an%20extensive%20waitlist%20of%20C-suite%20executives%20seeking%20his%20help%20with%20those%20tasks%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20technology%20is%20moving%20so%20fast%2C%20the%20gap%20between%20what%20CEOs%20need%20to%20know%20and%20what%20they%20actually%20understand%20is%20massive%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hopper%2C%20a%20former%20finance%20chief%20and%20author%20of%20the%202024%20book%20%26quot%3BAI%20Mastery%20for%20Finance%20Professionals%3A%20Foundations%2C%20Techniques%2C%20and%20Applications.%26quot%3B%20That's%20why%20so%20many%20bosses%20are%20knocking%20on%20his%20door%2C%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeadership%20coaches%20and%20consultants%20have%20long%20helped%20CEOs%20navigate%20the%20pressures%20of%20the%20corner%20office.%20Now%2C%20executive%20sherpas%20who%20were%20early%20to%20embrace%20AI%20say%20they're%20seeing%20a%20spike%20in%20CEOs%20seeking%20guidance%20on%20everything%20from%20vetting%20vendors%20and%20establishing%20safety%20protocols%20to%20preparing%20for%20the%20next%20big%20wave%20of%20AI%20breakthroughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20is%20inbound%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Conor%20Grennan%2C%20chief%20of%20AI%20Mindset%2C%20an%20AI%20consulting%20and%20training%20firm%20he%20founded%20in%202023.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20list%20a%20mile%20long.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrennan%2C%20also%20chief%20AI%20architect%20at%20New%20York%20University's%20Stern%20School%20of%20Business%2C%20said%20company%20leaders%20often%20reach%20out%20after%20struggling%20to%20get%20employees%20to%20adopt%20AI.%20They%20see%20other%20CEOs%20touting%20AI's%20benefits%2C%20and%20so%20they're%20feeling%20like%20they're%20behind%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223b3eb17f-1e3b-4784-a4c5-0c94a0cc8790%5C%22%3E'It%20was%20garbage%20in%2C%20garbage%20out'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20AI%20gurus%20that%20company%20leaders%20are%20tapping%20helm%20(or%20work%20at)%20startups%20that%20were%20launched%20in%20recent%20years%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20AI%20boom.%20Others%20head%20up%20new%20or%20expanded%20AI%20teams%20within%20established%20advisory%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELan%20Guan%20was%20named%20Accenture's%20first%20chief%20AI%20officer%20in%202023%2C%20two%20decades%20after%20joining%20the%20professional-services%20firm.%20She's%20since%20been%20counseling%20a%20growing%20number%20of%20company%20leaders%20on%20how%20to%20bring%20AI%20into%20their%20organizations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCEOs%20need%20an%20AI%20translator%20to%20basically%20sift%20through%20all%20this%20noise%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20amount%20of%20signals%20you're%20getting%2C%20the%20amount%20of%20noise%2C%20it's%20so%20distracting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompany%20leaders%20are%20also%20seeking%20out%20AI%20gurus%20in%20some%20cases%20to%20fix%20mistakes%20they%20made%20while%20going%20at%20it%20alone.%20Guan%20recalled%20one%20CEO%20who%20came%20to%20her%20after%20the%20person's%20company%20had%20to%20pause%20a%20multi-million%20dollar%20investment%20in%20a%20custom%20AI%20model%20because%20employees%20trained%20it%20on%20dozens%20of%20different%20versions%20of%20the%20same%20operating%20procedure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20they%20tried%20to%20scale%2C%20their%20data%20was%20not%20clean%20enough%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20garbage%20in%2C%20garbage%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmos%20Susskind%2C%20CEO%20and%20founder%20of%20the%20London%20beauty-tech%20startup%20Noli%2C%20has%20been%20tapping%20Guan%20and%20members%20of%20her%20team%20for%20AI-related%20guidance%20for%20the%20past%20year.%20Noli's%20roughly%2020%20employees%20have%20been%20using%20AI%20tools%20to%20do%20their%20jobs%20and%20the%20company's%20beauty-product%20recommendation%20platform%20is%20powered%20by%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20in%20touch%20with%20AI%20leaders%20in%20Accenture%20probably%20five%20times%20a%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Susskind%2C%20who%20previously%20led%20L'Oreal's%20consumer-products%20division%20for%20the%20U.K.%20and%20Ireland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221491a3dd-1df8-403f-9fa4-78e7dc4c812d%5C%22%3EShaping%20the%20AI%20narrative%20leaders%20use%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%2078%25%20of%20workers%20said%20their%20organizations%20had%20used%20AI%20in%20at%20least%20one%20function%2C%20up%20from%2055%25%20in%202023%2C%20according%20to%20a%20March%20survey%20by%20global%20management%20consulting%20firm%20McKinsey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20are%20planning%20to%20dig%20into%20AI%20even%20more%20this%20year.%20A%20May%20survey%20from%20professional-services%20firm%20PricewaterhouseCoopers%20found%20that%2088%25%20of%20senior%20executives%20planned%20to%20increase%20their%20AI-related%20budgets%20in%20the%20next%2012%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20is%20in%20line%20with%2C%20if%20not%20bigger%20than%2C%20the%20internet%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dan%20Priest%2C%20chief%20AI%20officer%20of%20PwC%2C%20whose%20position%20was%20created%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPublic%20company%20CEOs%20mentioned%20%26quot%3Bagentic%20AI%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20AI%20systems%20capable%20of%20acting%20autonomously%20%E2%80%94%20and%20similar%20terms%20on%20269%20conference%20calls%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%2C%20up%20from%2012%20during%20the%20same%20period%20last%20year%2C%20according%20to%20AI%20research%20firm%20AlphaSense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20those%20AI%20mentions%20right%20is%20another%20reason%20why%20company%20leaders%20are%20leaning%20on%20AI%20sages.%20CEOs%20need%20to%20consider%20more%20than%20just%20how%20investors%20and%20analysts%20interpret%20their%20remarks%2C%20said%20Priest.%20Employees%20are%20listening%2C%20too%2C%20and%20workplace%20experts%20say%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ceos-talk-ai-job-impact-employees-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheightened%20anxiety%3C%2Fa%3E%20among%20personnel%20can%20dent%20productivity%20and%20drive%20up%20turnover.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20want%20to%20be%20careful%2C%26quot%3B%20warned%20Priest%2C%20who%20helps%20CEOs%20communicate%20their%20AI%20strategy%20externally.%20%26quot%3BThe%20second%20you%20start%20talking%20about%20AI%20efficiencies%2C%20it%20makes%20your%20teams%20very%20nervous.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECEOs%20also%20need%20to%20make%20sure%20employees%20using%20AI%20are%20doing%20so%20safely%2C%20said%20Hopper%2C%20the%20AI%20strategist%20in%20Memphis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20try%20to%20have%20too%20prohibitive%20a%20policy%20or%20don't%20have%20a%20policy%20at%20all%2C%20that's%20when%20people%20are%20going%20to%20do%20stup