0locals%20told%20me%20that%20seasonal%20vegetables%20are%20no%20longer%20available%20in%20the%20markets%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Soumya%2C%20whose%20growing-up%20years%20in%20Sambalpur%2C%20Odisha%2C%20have%20given%20him%20a%20sound%20sense%20of%20local%20produce.%20%E2%80%9CNot%20only%20are%20the%20seasons%20delayed%2C%20they%20say%2C%20but%20even%20when%20they%20do%20arrive%2C%20they%20lack%20their%20characteristics%3B%20it%20rains%20in%20winter%2C%20summers%20are%20unbearably%20hot%2C%20and%20monsoons%20often%20pause%20to%20make%20way%20for%20%E2%80%98a%20summer%E2%80%99%20in%20between.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20cities%2C%20we%20call%20this%20global%20warming%2C%20a%20reality%20that%20the%20United%20Nations%20is%20racing%20against%20time%20to%20cap%20at%201.5%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20a%20threshold%20which%2C%20once%20crossed%2C%20could%20%E2%80%9Cunleash%20far%20more%20severe%20climate%20change%20impacts%2C%20including%20more%20frequent%20and%20severe%20droughts%2C%20heatwaves%2C%20and%20rainfall%E2%80%9D.%20The%20people%20across%20India%E2%80%99s%20rural%20pockets%20have%20a%20bone%20to%20pick%20with%20it%3B%20the%20shifting%20seasons%20have%20heralded%20uncertainty%20into%20their%20lives.%20But%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20paddy%20farmers%20who%20bear%20the%20brunt%20%E2%80%94%20rice%20covers%2069%20percent%20of%20the%20cultivable%20area%3B%20unseasonal%20rains%20incapacitate%20their%20farming%20patterns.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20harvest%20these%20days%20is%20less%20than%20half%20of%20what%20they%20previously%20achieved%2C%E2%80%9D%20Soumya%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20is%20clear%3A%20despite%20India%E2%80%99s%20hinterland%20experiencing%20some%20semblance%20of%20a%20climate%20crisis%2C%20many%20lack%20the%20vocabulary%20to%20articulate%20it.%20And%20it%20is%20not%20their%20fault%2C%20says%20Jagadish%20Thaker%2C%20a%20senior%20lecturer%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Queensland%2C%20Australia%2C%20and%20principal%20investigator%20of%20a%202023%2