%99s%20a%20way%20of%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-twitter%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EA%20beautiful%20family%20of%20elephants%20moves%20with%20their%20little%20ones%20somewhere%20in%20Nilgiris.%20The%20annual%20migration%20season%20of%20elephants%20from%20deciduous%20forests%20of%20Karnataka%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20to%20Moist%20ever%20green%20forests%20of%20Kerala%20has%20begun%20as%20summer%20is%20setting%20in%20this%20part%20of%20the%20western%20Ghats.%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FXPHXCcbSJz%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FXPHXCcbSJz%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Supriya%20Sahu%20IAS%20(%40supriyasahuias)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsupriyasahuias%2Fstatus%2F1752638812029915435%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2031%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20stories%20may%20not%20flood%20your%20newsfeed%2C%20but%20they%20matter.%20Because%20in%20each%20of%20them%2C%20ordinary%20people%20made%20a%20critical%20decision%20to%20act%20responsibly%20rather%20than%20react%20impulsively.%20And%20that%20single%20decision%20made%20all%20the%20difference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20it%20matters%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUrban%20wildlife%20encounters%20are%20not%20just%20a%20side%20effect%20of%20development.%20Instead%2C%C2%A0%20they%E2%80%99re%20a%20mirror%20to%20how%20we%20treat%20the%20world%20beyond%20our%20cities.%20These%20animals%20don%E2%80%99t%20enter%20our%20streets%20by%20choice.%20Often%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20displaced%2C%20disoriented%2C%20or%20desperate%20for%20food%20and%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20the%20next%20time%20you%20spot%20a%2